701867f-a.title: Bronx: Stillwell Avenue - Gunther Avenue
701867f-a.text:
Stillwell Ave. (right), north side, east from Gunther to Wickhaw
Aves., showing new homes in the residential development known as Pelham
Parkway Gardens. Also shown (left) is the east side of Gunther Ave.,
north from Stillwell to Astor Aves.
About 1923.
Jsoeph P. Day.

701869f.text:

About 1923.

701202f-b.title: Bronx: Gunther Avenue - Stillwell Avenue
701202f-b.text:
2226-2232 Gunther Ave., east side, between Stillwell and Astor Aves.,
showing a 2-family dwelling in the residential district known as Pelham
Parkway Gardens. The numbers 16 and 17, on the door fronts, refer to the
1ot numbers on which the two sections of the dwelling are located; the
picture having been taken before the house was sold.
About 1923.
Kenneth Clark.
